  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK551">
<l>kolaimēṟkoṇ ṭāriṟ koṭitē yalaimēlkoṇ </l>
<l> ṭallavai ceytoḻukum vēntu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The king who gives himself up to oppression and acts unjustly (towards his subjects) is more cruel than the man who leads the life of a murderer.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
